---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import CtaBand from '../../components/CtaBand.astro'
---
<BaseLayout
  title="What Is LiveMap™? — VPick+"
  description="Learn how LiveMap provides real-time picker visibility across the DC floor using the VPick+ location field."
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb container" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="separator">›</span>
    <a href="/learn">Learn</a><span class="separator">›</span>
    <span aria-current="page">What Is LiveMap™?</span>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-wrap">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <h1>What Is LiveMap™?</h1>
        <p class="lead">Real-time visibility across the distribution center — see exactly where pickers are working as tasks update.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/livemap-banner.png" alt="LiveMap real-time DC visibility" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h2>Why LiveMap™ Matters</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Supervisors need real-time clarity — not delayed reports. LiveMap™ gives operations leaders a constantly updating picture of where pickers are inside the DC.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Balance work across zones based on live movement</li>
        <li>Reduce congestion before it slows picking</li>
        <li>See active vs idle time without walking the floor</li>
        <li>Monitor throughput visually, as it happens</li>
        <li>Increase supervisor reach in large DC environments</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h2>How LiveMap™ Works</h2>
      <p>
        LiveMap™ uses the existing <strong>VPick+ location field</strong>, updated automatically as each picker completes tasks. Every confirmation includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Aisle location</li>
        <li>Bay location</li>
        <li>Timestamp</li>
        <li>Picker ID</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These updates power a real-time map that shows pickers moving across the floor — without needing Bluetooth beacons, RTLS hardware, or sensors.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/vpick#livemap">View LiveMap™ on the Product Page</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:info@vpickplus.us?subject=LiveMap%20Demo%20Request" style="margin-left:8px;">See your DC live</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand />
</BaseLayout>
